premise_source_doc_sentence: The company was founded by Maria Costeira and Ami Dror in 1995 as X6D Limited .
StreetDance 3D  (  also called StreetDance in the non-3D version  )  is a 2010 British 3D dance drama film which was released on 21 May 2010 .
The first home video game console to be capable of 3D was the Sega Master System in which a limited number of titles were capable of delivering 3D .
Now there are several competing digital 3D formats including Dolby 3D , XpanD 3D , Panavision 3D , MasterImage 3D and IMAX 3D .

Step Up 3D premiered in Hollywood at the El Capitan Theater on August 2 , 2010 and was subsequently released worldwide on August 6 , 2010 , through conventional 2D and 3D  (  in RealD 3D , Dolby 3D , and XpanD 3D  )  formats .
